{"type":"message","id":"0bcf341d","parentId":"41f1ccac","timestamp":"2026-04-10T08:59:42.803Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the picture clearly:\n\n1. **My session (main agent)** - The current session `agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb` was just updated at `2026-04-10 16:59:15` - that's TODAY, right now. This session IS being recorded.\n\n2. **Product-selector subagent** - The session `agent:product-selector:feishu:direct:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb` was last updated at `2026-03-27 20:06:43` - almost 2 weeks ago! And its `sessionFile` points to `/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/product-selector/sessions/f3bca540-ab50-43ce-bd5f-8dd126caefe6.jsonl` which doesn't exist (the actual file is in `agents/main/product-selector/sessions/`).\n   \nThe subagent sessions aren't being recorded - they show `compactionCount: null` and either point to non-existent files or have no file path at all, whereas my session has an actual file location and proper compaction tracking.\n\nThe product-selector agent runs once per request and stops, so there's no persistent session between calls, and even if there were, the session file path in the config points to a location that doesn't exist on the actual filesystem.\n\nBut the real issue is the product-selector is configured as a subagent with `spawnMode: \"run\"` rather than `\"session\"` mode, which means it launches fresh each time without any conversation history being maintained."},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 对比一下就清楚了：\n\n**我（main agent）的 session：**\n- ✅ 今天 16:59 刚更新，文件存在：`agents/main/sessions/a4b0ebf9-...jsonl`\n- compactionCount: 0（正常）\n\n**product-selector 的 session：**\n- ❌ 上次更新 3月27日，距今快两周\n- 文件路径指向 `/agents/product-selector/sessions/...` 但实际文件在 `/agents/main/product-selector/sessions/`——**路径对不上**\n- compactionCount: 0\n\n**结论：我的存储是正常的，product-selector 那边有问题。**\n\n问题根源是 product-selector 配置的是 `spawnMode: \"run\"`（一次性运行），不是 `\"session\"`（保持会话）。所以每次调用它都是空白启动，没有上下文继承。\n\n你要修的是 product-selector 的配置，把 `spawnMode: \"run\"` 改成 `spawnMode: \"session\"`，并且修复 sessions.json 里的路径。要我直接改吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775811564398,"responseId":"0627eeecdc8f85a9bc7a1b138dcb9d28"}}
