{"type":"message","id":"f2ae229e","parentId":"73cd5815","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:42:18.864Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-10 17:42:14 GMT+8] Feishu[kiit] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b52b81192f484b39a7c86a1dae15]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52b81192f484b39a7c86a1dae15\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 17:42 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n先给结论：最优方案是选「A + 解决冲突」，直接把两个问题一次性根治，不丢功能\n一、问题拆解&根因\n\n1. memory-lancedb API key 错误\n\n• 根因：官方基础版 memory-lancedb 默认只认 OpenAI 格式的 embedding key，你现在填的是 MiniMax 的 key，格式不匹配，直接失效\n\n• 影响：向量检索完全失效，Agent 只能靠关键词搜记忆，准确率暴跌\n\n2. openviking 工具名冲突\n\n• 根因：openviking 和 memory-lancedb 都注册了 memory_recall/memory_search 同名工具，4.9 版本做了工具名校验，直接报错\n\n• 影响：两个插件互相抢工具，导致记忆系统启动异常\n二、完整解决方案（一步到位，不丢功能）\n\n🔧 第一步：给 memory-lancedb 配置正确的 MiniMax embedding（解决 key 错误）\n\n4.9 版本支持自定义 embedding 提供商，不用换 OpenAI key，直接用你现有的 MiniMax：\n\n1. 打开配置文件 ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n\n2. 找到 plugins.entries.memory-lancedb 节点，修改为：\n\"memory-lancedb\": {\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"config\": {\n    \"embedding\": {\n      \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n      \"model\": \"embo-01\",\n      \"apiKey\": \"${MINIMAX_API_KEY}\",\n      \"baseURL\": \"https://api.minimax.chat/v1/embeddings\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n3. 确保你的 MiniMax key 已经在全局配置里：\n\"models\": {\n  \"providers\": {\n    \"minimax\": {\n      \"apiKey\": \"你的MiniMax API Key\",\n      \"enabled\": true\n    }\n  }\n}\n🔧 第二步：解决 openviking 工具名冲突（两个插件共存）\n\n4.9 版本支持工具别名，直接给 openviking 重命名，避免和 lancedb 冲突：\n\n1. 在 plugins.entries.openviking 里添加工具重命名配置：\n\"openviking\": {\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"config\": {\n    \"memoryPath\": \"~/.openclaw/openviking-memory\",\n    \"toolPrefix\": \"openviking_\",\n    \"excludeTools\": [\"memory_recall\", \"memory_search\"]\n  }\n}\n2. 同时在全局配置里指定记忆后端为 openviking，让 lancedb 只做向量存储，不抢工具：\n\"memory\": {\n  \"backend\": \"openviking\",\n  \"vectorStore\": \"memory-lancedb\"\n}\n🔧 第三步：重启网关生效\nopenclaw gateway restart\n三、三个方案对比（帮你做选择）\n方案 操作 优点 缺点 适合场景 \nA（推荐） 给 lancedb 配置 MiniMax + 给 openviking 重命名 两个插件全开，功能拉满，不丢任何能力 需改2处配置，1分钟搞定 你现在的选品Agent，需要长记忆+向量检索双buff \nB 禁用 openviking，只留 lancedb + memory-core 操作最简单，零配置 丢失长记忆压缩，Token成本飙升，长对话容易失忆 临时应急，不推荐长期用 \nC 查原 embedding key 无实际收益，只是确认问题 浪费时间，解决不了根本问题 仅排查用，不推荐 \n\n四、验证是否成功\n\n重启后执行：\n# 1. 确认插件状态正常\nopenclaw plugins list\n# 2. 测试记忆检索\nopenclaw chat \"测试记忆召回\"\n# 3. 查看日志无报错\nopenclaw logs --tail 50\n• 三个插件状态均为 enabled\n\n• 记忆检索正常，无 key 错误、无工具冲突报错\n\n• 就是完全正常的状态\n五、给你的最终建议\n\n直接选方案A，一次性把两个问题都解决，保留全部功能\n\n• 不用换 OpenAI key，继续用你现有的 MiniMax\n\n• 两个插件共存，lancedb 做向量存储，openviking 做长记忆压缩，完美适配你的选品Agent\n\n• 配置改完，重启一次就永久生效，不用再折腾"}],"timestamp":1775814138847}}
{"type":"message","id":"34856ce2","parentId":"f2ae229e","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:42:39.707Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is sending me what appears to be a very detailed analysis/prescription for fixing the two issues. It looks like they might have gotten this from somewhere (maybe an AI assistant or documentation) and want me to implement it.\n\nHowever, I should be careful here. This analysis mentions:\n1. `provider: \"minimax\"` and `model: \"embo-01\"` for lancedb embedding - but I need to verify if memory-lancedb actually supports these config options (it might not)\n2. `toolPrefix: \"openviking_\"` and `excludeTools` for openviking - need to verify if these config options actually exist\n3. A `memory.backend` and `memory.vectorStore` config structure\n\nSome of these config options might be made up or not actually supported by the plugins. I should verify what the plugins actually support before blindly applying.\n\nLet me check:\n1. What config options memory-lancedb actually supports\n2. What config options openviking actually supports\n3. Whether these proposed options are real\n\nFrom what I saw earlier in the memory-lancedb openclaw.plugin.json:\n- embedding.apiKey\n- embedding.model\n- embedding.baseUrl\n- embedding.dimensions\n- dbPath\n- autoCapture\n- autoRecall\n- captureMaxChars\n\nThere's no `provider` field, and there's no `toolPrefix` or `excludeTools` in the schema I saw.\n\nThe user's \"conclusion\" suggests implementing Option A, but some of the specific config fields might not exist. I should be honest about this and not make up configuration.\n\nLet me verify what's actually available before proceeding."},{"type":"text","text":"这个分析很详细，但有些配置项需要核实是不是真的存在。让我先验证一下：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2glvsnhovuyb_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/halei/.openclaw/extensions/openviking/openclaw.plugin.json 2>/dev/null || find /home/halei/.openclaw/extensions/openviking