{"type":"message","id":"814b930b","parentId":"b98c5c97","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:43:03.545Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the actual schemas. The user's proposed solution mentions:\n\n1. `provider: \"minimax\"` for lancedb embedding - the schema doesn't have a `provider` field, only `apiKey`, `model`, `baseUrl`, `dimensions`\n2. `toolPrefix` and `excludeTools` for openviking - the openviking schema doesn't have these fields either\n\nThe lancedb plugin supports `embedding.baseUrl` which could work for MiniMax. Let me check if MiniMax has an embedding endpoint.\n\nAlso, openviking has `autoRecall` and `autoCapture` but the tool conflict is about `memory_recall` and `memory_search` tools. \n\nThese are standard tools registered by the memory plugins themselves. The real issue is that multiple plugins are trying to register the same tool names, so the proposed solution of using `toolPrefix` or `excludeTools` won't actually work since those parameters don't exist in the schemas. I need to figure out if there's a way to disable specific tools or if I should just disable openviking entirely to prevent the conflicts. Looking at the plugin schemas more carefully, memory-lancedb has `embedding.apiKey`, `embedding.model`, `embedding.baseUrl`, and `embedding.dimensions`, while openviking supports `mode`, `configPath`, `port`, `baseUrl`, `apiKey`, and `targetUri` — so neither actually has the `toolPrefix` or `excludeTools` fields mentioned in the issue. I think the best path forward is to recommend disabling openviking and properly configuring lancedb's embedding to work with MiniMax's API instead."},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 你给的方案思路对，但有些字段在这两个插件的 schema 里**并不存在**。让我对照真实 schema 核实一下：\n\n**lancedb 支持的 embedding 字段**：\n- `apiKey` ✅\n- `model` ✅\n- `baseUrl` ✅（可自定义端点）\n- `dimensions` ✅\n- **没有 `provider` 字段**\n\n**openviking 支持的字段**：\n- 各种配置项都有\n- **没有 `toolPrefix` 和 `excludeTools` 字段**\n\n---\n\n所以方案要调整：**lancedb 用 MiniMax embedding 可以，但需要通过 `baseUrl` 指向 MiniMax 的嵌入端点**，而不是用 `provider` 字段。openviking 的冲突没有简单的排除字段。\n\n**实际可行的最优方案**：\n\n1. **lancedb**：把 `baseUrl` 改成 `https://api.minimax.chat/v1/embeddings`，model 改成 `embo-01`（MiniMax 的嵌入模型），保持 `apiKey` 不变\n2. **openviking**：目前没有工具排除机制，工具冲突没有官方解法，只能二选一\n\n你想：\n- **A**：保留 lancedb（配 MiniMax embedding），禁用 openviking\n- **B**：保留 openviking（它本身有 recall/store 功能），禁用 lancedb\n- **C**：两个都开但先不解决冲突，看实际影响大不大"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775814159911,"responseId":"0627f9105b8898b680b3fe08258e0444"}}
